    <div class="middle"> 
     <h2>Professor of <a href="http://www.cs.ucl.ac.uk/staff/A.Finkelstein/defn.html">Software Systems Engineering</a><p></p></h2> 
     <p>My programme of research and scholarly activity is based at <a href="https://turing.ac.uk/">The Alan Turing Institute</a>, the UK National Institute for the Data Sciences.<br><br> </p>
     <p>I am located at <a href="https://turing.ac.uk/">The Alan Turing Institute</a> labs in <a href="http://www.bl.uk/">The British Library</a>. A PGP Public Key [for research and academic work] can be obtained <a href="http://www.cs.ucl.ac.uk/staff/A.Finkelstein/pgpkey.txt">here</a>.</p>
     <br> 
     <p></p>EMail: a.finkelstein[at]ucl.ac.uk or afinkelstein[at]turing.ac.uk
     <p></p>Skype: anthonyfinkelstein 
     <p></p>Linkedin: 
     <a href="http://www.linkedin.com/pub/anthony-finkelstein/0/174/15">Anthony Finkelstein</a> 
     <p></p>
     <br> Mail Only:
     <p></p>University College London 
     <p></p>Department of Computer Science 
     <p></p>Gower Street 
     <p></p>London WC1E 6BT, United Kingdom 
